  <summary>Play draughts (checkers) with 16 variants, AI opponents, and online multiplayer</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Draughts is a comprehensive checkers/draughts game featuring 16 international game variants,
      multiple AI difficulty levels, online multiplayer, and a beautiful modern interface built with GTK4 and LibAdwaita.
      Whether you're a casual player or a serious competitor, Draughts offers engaging gameplay
      for players of all skill levels - play against AI, friends locally, or opponents online!
    </p>
    <p>Game Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>16 international draughts variants including American Checkers, International Draughts, Russian, Brazilian, and more</li>
      <li>10 AI difficulty levels from Beginner to Grandmaster</li>
      <li>Online multiplayer with quick match, room hosting, and session persistence</li>
      <li>Human vs Human (local and online), Human vs AI, and AI vs AI gameplay modes</li>
      <li>Complete move history with undo/redo support</li>
      <li>PDN (Portable Draughts Notation) export for game analysis</li>
      <li>Multiple board themes and piece styles (plastic, wood, metal, bottle-cap)</li>
      <li>Timer modes: countdown, Fischer increment, and Bronstein delay</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Accessibility and Polish:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Sound effects for moves, captures, and game events</li>
      <li>Keyboard navigation and screen reader support</li>
      <li>High contrast mode for better visibility</li>
      <li>Smooth animations and visual feedback</li>
      <li>Game history browser with replay functionality</li>
      <li>Comprehensive rules documentation for each variant</li>
      <li>Adaptive board orientation - your pieces always at the bottom</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
